text: Nandita Adhiya (born 6 January 1978) is a Gujarati cricketer. She played for Saurashtra women and West Zone women. She has played 27 Limited over matches and 10 Women's Twenty20. == References == Category:Saurashtra women cricketers Category:West Zone women cricketers Category:1978 births Category:People from Gujarat Category:Living people
